        "TileImage": "$($repository f19cb43e-7f33-4d27-aa42-ecd7918eb2fe).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. \rWe have received intel that a corporation has been researching and developing a viral contagion in a hospital located in Hokkaido and is planning on releasing it during the upcoming resort festival.\r\r Your targets are all involved in this conspiracy in one way or another. You have also been authorised to find and eliminate Carlton Smith, who we suspect is being forced into being a patient zero for this outbreak.\rGood luck, 47.",
